</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-33_ pf-text-1">The Care Quality Commission (CQC) oversees the regulation and inspection of adult social care providers in England, ensuring compliance with quality and safety standards.



</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-35_ pf-text-1">Local authorities in England spent approximately Â£18.2 billion on adult social care in 2019/20, highlighting the substantial investment in this sector.




</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-37_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-38_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-39_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key definitions
</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-41_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-42_ pf-text-1"><strong>Adult social care</strong> - It encompasses a range of services designed to support adults with physical or learning disabilities, mental health issues, or those who require assistance due to age-related frailty.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-44_ pf-text-1"><strong>Personal care</strong> - Assistance with washing, dressing, and toileting tasks, promoting independence and maintaining dignity.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-46_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-47_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-48_ pf-heading-1-h3">Legislation, regulations, and best practice</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-50_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-51_ pf-text-1"><strong></strong><strong>The Care Act 2014</strong> - This landmark legislation sets out the legal framework for adult social care in England, emphasising person-centred approaches, prevention, and integration of health and social care services.


