</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-55_ pf-text-1"><strong>National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) guidelines </strong>- Provide evidence-based guidance on various aspects of adult social care, including dementia care, end-of-life support, and mental health interventions.






