</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-66_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-67_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-68_ pf-heading-1-h3">Ensuring quality and safety</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-70_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-71_ pf-text-1"><strong>Staff training and development</strong> - Equipping care staff with the necessary skills and knowledge through ongoing training programs, enhancing the quality of care delivery.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-73_ pf-text-1"><strong>Safeguarding measures</strong> - Implementing robust safeguarding policies and procedures to protect vulnerable adults from abuse and neglect.
